OL,3,CScotland's Finance Secretary lays out
OL,4,Cdemands ahead of Budget
OL,6,FShe called for action to lower
OL,7,Fhousehold energy bills, to ensure that
OL,8,Fany major taxation choices do not see
OL,9,FScotland losing out on vital funding,
OL,10,Fand to reform the energy profits levy
OL,11,Fto support jobs and investment across
OL,12,FScotland's energy sector.
OL,14,FMs Robison said: "The UK Budget
OL,15,Fprocess has been chaotic and mired in
OL,16,Fdamaging uncertainty.
OL,18,F"It is disappointing that neither the
OL,19,FPrime Minister nor the Chancellor were
OL,20,Fable to meet with the First Minister
OL,21,Fin London this week.
