OL,3,CScotland's Finance Secretary lays out
OL,4,Cdemands ahead of Budget
OL,6,F"Given the limited time to consider
OL,7,Fthe implications of any major policy
OL,8,Fchanges between the UK Budget and the
OL,9,FScottish Budget on January 13, this
OL,10,Flack of engagement is a particular
OL,11,Fconcern.
OL,13,F"Last year, the UK Government
OL,14,Fincreased employer national insurance
OL,15,Fcontributions without any
OL,16,Fconsultation, which led to a funding
OL,17,Fshortfall of around #400 million for
OL,18,Fpublic services in Scotland and acts
OL,19,Fas a tax on jobs.
OL,21,F"We cannot see a repeat this year.
