OL,3,CScotland's Finance Secretary lays out
OL,4,Cdemands ahead of Budget
OL,6,F"We need to see a change of course
OL,7,Ffrom the Chancellor ` with investment
OL,8,Fin public services and infrastructure,
OL,9,Fwhich supports industry and jobs and
OL,10,Fdelivers support on the cost-of-living
OL,11,Fchallenges people across Scotland are
OL,12,Ffacing."
OL,14,FShe added: "Energy bills in particular
OL,15,Fare a source of real worry for people
OL,16,Fthis winter.
