OL,3,CScotland's Finance Secretary lays out
OL,4,Cdemands ahead of Budget
OL,6,F"While the UK Government promised to
OL,7,Fcut energy bills by #300, they have
OL,8,Factually risen by almost #200 ` so
OL,9,Fthis Budget must provide some relief
OL,10,Ffor households who are struggling.
OL,12,F"The UK Government must also listen to
OL,13,Findustry concerns around the energy
OL,14,Fprofits levy.
OL,16,F"This was always supposed to be a
OL,17,Ftemporary measure and it is now
OL,18,Faffecting investment and jobs in
OL,19,FScotland.
