OL,3,CScotland's Finance Secretary lays out
OL,4,Cdemands ahead of Budget
OL,6,F"The UK Government needs to set out
OL,7,Fhow a stable and long-term fiscal
OL,8,Fregime will be used to treat the
OL,9,Foffshore energy sector fairly,
OL,10,Falongside other parts of the UK
OL,11,Feconomy, and deliver business and
OL,12,Finvestor certainty.
OL,14,F"Scotland must not be left as an
OL,15,Fafterthought yet again in the UK
OL,16,FBudget."
